{"tid":938222,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★旺角消防局外旅巴撞途人　消防走出救援","createTime":"2018-12-12T06:47:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-12T08:01:41.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c7efbec32476260ccd48282d4ffbb9c7291b3c29","tid":938222,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T06:47:35.000Z","msg":"今日(12日)中午12時許，一輛旅遊巴沿太子塘尾道往深水埗方向行駛，當駛至旺角消防局對開時，撞倒一名過路男途人。消防員聞訊由局內走到現場拯救，傷者其後由救護車送院。意外原因有待警方調查。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181212/photo/bkn-20181212141619184-1212_00822_001_01p.jpg?20181212143630\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181212%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181212141619184-1212_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20181212143630&h=74045ee2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181212/bkn-20181212141619184-1212_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181212%2Fbkn-20181212141619184-1212_00822_001.html&d=3LHRZsUT7ChIVUMdJzdIt4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=e5de15d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181212/bkn-20181212141619184-1212_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"9e93b7118686ad9159534a653f3965e103e8f293","tid":938222,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T06:47:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1255c7cae0d217af5b4c147d951e2bf6c1a79a8e","tid":938222,"uid":29606,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T07:02:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"17d94c6c5dd65de97557ec89e2efc67eeedf330b","tid":938222,"uid":47112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T07:03:55.000Z","msg":"方便 快捷"},{"pid":"038d660131250e2e3d72ab678422d2ba334e0b0b","tid":938222,"uid":18241,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T07:17:02.000Z","msg":"諗起醫院門口暈低叫你自己報警<img src